id":1439324,"uid":294516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:50:26.000Z","msg":"Pish <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05404df1a2227a6077eb568dfb1e53afbb3ab4bb","tid":1439324,"uid":294516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:46:53.000Z","msg":"Pish <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9d5e2e11b660bb864d682e84567d0eefabb23f5","tid":1439324,"uid":294516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:57:48.000Z","msg":"真。對準政權系列：中國共產黨不想香港人知道的秘密<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1437411\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1437411</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中國經濟真係好大問題 而且國內各個階層一定會有曾經被共產黨打壓既人，會有反共意識。所以輸出革命意識一定要係我地其中一樣落力要做既事，我地要珍惜呢個機會，瓦解中國共產政權！"},{"pid":"d2fbff8aebc3a964d1380105e4d9a04a27877b81","tid":1439324,"uid":294516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:03:08.000Z","msg":"Pish!"},{"pid":"59ba0629bb8da47ff2df08560768fba746805b09","tid":1439324,"uid":294516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:39:40.000Z","msg":"繼續推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adc99898a972a7018d35e9a3328fd5bb85f03eef","tid":1439324,"uid":294516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:27:10.000Z","msg":"個天都幫我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「突發」浙江出現超歷史性大洪水 官娱呼籲緊急疏散！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1440768\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1440768</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d69426bfcbed8826fc63139779902528b8be3625","tid":1439324,"uid":294516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:08:19.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"afecb8e5593264eb86170ab68979df4583e3d3e7","tid":1439324,"uid":294516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite